- [ ] app.py — Flask application code
- [ ] models.py — SQLAlchemy model definitions
- [ ] routes.py — Flask route definitions
- [ ] tests/test_app.py — pytest test file

## Test Command
make test

## Dependencies
python3, pip, flask, sqlalchemy, pytest
